description: Welcome to this stunning 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo, built in 2017 and ideally located just a 5-minute walk to the Red Line. Designed for both style and functionality, the open-concept layout features a massive kitchen island—perfect for cooking, dining, and entertaining. The living space is flooded with natural light from 11-foot floor-to-ceiling windows, so bright we didn’t even need the lights on during the photo shoot. Enjoy in-unit laundry, central air, and the rare benefit of garage parking. Professionally managed, this building offers effortless, low-maintenance living in a prime South Boston location with easy access to downtown, shops, and restaurants. An exceptional opportunity for first-time buyers, investors, or anyone seeking a move-in-ready home in one of the city’s most vibrant & growing neighborhoods.
